One person has died and another has sustained moderate injuries. This is after their bakkie overturned several times along the R56 in Thornville, Pietermaritzburg this morning. This happened shortly after 7.30 am. ER24 spokesman, Werner Vermaak said paramedics from ER24 arrived on the scene where they found the bakkie lying on its side several meters into an open veld. He said upon assessment, they found a man, believed to be 23-years-old, next to the road.     